Vodka Market, Global Outlook and Forecast 2023-2030

The global Vodka market was valued at US$ 48000 million in 2022 and is projected to reach US$ 58110 million by 2029, at a CAGR of 2.8% during the forecast period. The influence of COVID-19 and the Russia-Ukraine War were considered while estimating market sizes

Vodka is a mixture of purified water and rectified ethyl alcohol. Vodka is traditionally the product of distillation of fermented grains or potatoes. However, these days many modern brands use other substances such as fruits or sugar.

